data.text: RUSSIAN ATHLETES INELIGIBLE FOR PARTICIPATION IN INTERNATIONAL COMPETITIONS DURING THE SUSPENSION OF THE ALL RUSSIAN ATHLETICS FEDERATION (ARAF) Following the suspension of the All Russian Athletics Federation (ARAF) from membership of the IAAF, the following is intended as a list for meeting organisers of Russian athletes who are ineligible to compete during the period of the suspension (other than in national competitions organised in Russia). The list has been compiled from names received from ARAF having an affiliation to the Russian Athletics Federation and names included in the IAAF database. This list is not exhaustive.
